# Aluno: Rodrigo Vaisam Bastos

### Verbo GET – listar todos
GET http://localhost:8000/cliente/ HTTP/1.1

### Verbo GET – listar um
GET http://localhost:8000/cliente/2 HTTP/1.1

### Verbo POST – adiciona outro
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/cliente/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Cleiton",
    "cpf": "111.222.333-44",
    "telefone": "12345678901"
}

### Verbo POST – adicionar nome do aluno
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/cliente/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Rodrigo Vaisam Bastos",
    "cpf": "222.333.444-55",
    "telefone": "12345678901"
}

### Verbo PUT – atualiza o anterior criado
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/cliente/2 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Digo"
}

### Verbo PUT – atualiza outro qualquer
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/cliente/2 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Gersinho",
    "cpf": "123.333.444-55",
    "telefone": "12322233344"
}

### Verbo DELETE - excluir outro qualquer
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/cliente/3 HTTP/1.1

### Verbo DELETE - excluir o editado/criado
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/cliente/2 HTTP/1.1